Description: This package includes README and vignettes driving examples for spatial omics
	demonstrations in NHGRI AnVIL.  Canonical experiments are retrieved from cloud
	and cached.  Vignettes illustrate key functionalities as they emerge in development.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0), tools, utils, SpatialData, SpatialData.plot, Rarr (>= 1.7.1)
